495
00:34:08,813 --> 00:34:10,178
It's Tommy Donnelly.

496
00:34:10,348 --> 00:34:12,282
Tommy Donnelly.

497
00:34:13,017 --> 00:34:14,006
Okay.

498
00:34:15,186 --> 00:34:17,347
The stairs are
in the back.

499
00:34:17,655 --> 00:34:18,849
This way?
Yeah.

500
00:34:19,357 --> 00:34:20,847
Thanks.

