I'll be back in a minute.

506
00:34:40,845 --> 00:34:42,312
I'll be here.

507
00:34:42,380 --> 00:34:44,314
Anything happens,

508
00:34:44,649 --> 00:34:45,911
I'll be here.

509
00:34:59,597 --> 00:35:00,495
(KNOCKING)

510
00:35:01,365 --> 00:35:02,525
NICKY: Come in.

511
00:35:06,637 --> 00:35:08,195
Take a seat.

512
00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:16,674
You want a drink?

513
00:35:18,749 --> 00:35:19,773
No.

514
00:35:19,851 --> 00:35:20,977
No, thanks.

515
00:35:25,289 --> 00:35:26,984
I heard about Sal.

516
00:35:27,592 --> 00:35:28,786
I'm sorry.

517
00:35:29,393 --> 00:35:31,122
Yeah, it's a real loss.

518
00:35:34,532 --> 00:35:36,124
You here to pay
your respects?

