Louie Downtown.

521
00:35:46,043 --> 00:35:47,476
My brother's a junkie.

522
00:35:47,545 --> 00:35:49,274
Never thinks things through.

523
00:35:50,047 --> 00:35:51,639
So I took him to rehab,

524
00:35:52,150 --> 00:35:53,344
and I let Louie go.

525
00:35:54,452 --> 00:35:56,545
In the hopes
that it would end things.

526
00:35:57,321 --> 00:35:58,879
I don't want
any bad blood.

527
00:36:01,225 --> 00:36:02,920
There's 30,000 in there.

528
00:36:04,629 --> 00:36:07,462
With Sal gone,
I assume it belongs to you.

529
00:36:09,200 --> 00:36:10,497
Where's Louie?

530
00:36:12,103 --> 00:36:13,570
Don't know.

531
00:36:13,638 --> 00:36:15,196
Like I said,
I let him go.

532
00:36:16,040 --> 00:36:18,065
Every day Louie's missing,
I lose money.

533
00:36:20,545 --> 00:36:21,910
Tell you what
I'm gonna do.

534
00:36:23,414 --> 00:36:25,314
I'm gonna accept
this money in good faith.

535
00:36:26,384 --> 00:36:27,681
I appreciate it.

536
00:36:28,052 --> 00:36:31,317
But I need you to pay me
$1,000 a week until
Louie gets back.

537
00:36:32,590 --> 00:36:34,558
For disruption of business.

538
00:36:36,127 --> 00:36:37,617
You understand?

539
00:36:39,697 --> 00:36:41,164
That money makes us even.

540
00:36:42,767 --> 00:36:45,167
You got a lost bookie,
that's your problem.

541
00:36:46,370 --> 00:36:47,667
See you around.

542
00:36:48,839 --> 00:36:49,965
Hey, kid!

543
00:36:50,608 --> 00:36:52,633
Tell your brother Jimmy

544
00:36:52,710 --> 00:36:54,507
I'm gonna be seeing him
real soon.

545
00:36:54,679 --> 00:36:55,976
That'd be great.

546
00:36:56,347 --> 00:36:58,212
He'd enjoy the visitor.

547
00:36:59,417 --> 00:37:00,679
Didn't you hear?

548
00:37:01,018 --> 00:37:02,849
Jimmy was arrested yesterday.

549
00:37:03,721 --> 00:37:05,416
He's been in jail.

550
00:37:15,099 --> 00:37:17,829
And one more time,
you know this because...

551
00:37:17,935 --> 00:37:18,924
Oh, yeah.

552
00:37:19,737 --> 00:37:21,136
I was there, too.

553
00:37:30,081 --> 00:37:31,810
How'd it go?
Like it went.

554
00:37:34,352 --> 00:37:35,979
What the hell's
Joey Ice Cream doing here?

555
00:37:38,556 --> 00:37:40,046
I have no idea.

556
00:37:44,228 --> 00:37:47,755
<i>JOEY. We were that tight.</i>
<i>They never took</i>
<i>a step without me.</i>

557
00:38:01,512 --> 00:38:06,142
<i>JOEY. Remember when I said</i>
<i>how as a kid Tommy Donnelly</i>
<i>tried to make that deal?</i>

558
00:38:07,518 --> 00:38:09,281
<i>Well, God didn't hear him</i>
<i>right away.</i>

559
00:38:10,755 --> 00:38:12,723
<i>So Tommy kept going back.</i>

560
00:38:14,091 --> 00:38:16,355
<i>Kept trying</i>
<i>to get God's attention.</i>

561
00:38:18,129 --> 00:38:20,222
<i>Until He finally listened.</i>

562
00:38:22,066 --> 00:38:23,829
Your mom's looking for you.

563
00:38:25,069 --> 00:38:27,264
The doctor said
Jimmy's gonna walk.

564
00:38:34,545 --> 00:38:38,003
<i>Only thing is, Tommy never</i>
<i>negotiated the price.</i>

565
00:39:36,540 --> 00:39:38,303
I should have
told you last night.

566
00:39:38,376 --> 00:39:39,866
I love you.

567
00:40:18,616 --> 00:40:20,607
You got customers waiting?

568
00:40:28,926 --> 00:40:30,484
Glad you came by.

569
00:40:32,997 --> 00:40:34,225
Yeah. Me, too.

570
00:40:35,966 --> 00:40:38,161
Because I wanted
to tell you that I can't...

571
00:40:39,170 --> 00:40:40,364
Can't what?

572
00:40:40,905 --> 00:40:42,065
Do this.

573
00:40:42,706 --> 00:40:44,173
Be with you.

574
00:40:49,346 --> 00:40:50,745
I really am sorry.

575
00:40:56,120 --> 00:40:57,280
Wait.

576
00:40:57,388 --> 00:40:58,480
Jenny...

577
00:41:04,228 --> 00:41:05,752
If you want breakfast,
come on down.

578
00:41:12,603 --> 00:41:15,663
<i>JOEY. There was no way for him</i>
<i>to know way back then</i>

579
00:41:15,739 --> 00:41:19,539
<i>that God was gonna</i>
<i>take away the one thing</i>
<i>Tommy wanted most.</i>

580
00:41:26,784 --> 00:41:29,582
<i>But that's what life is like,</i>
<i>am I right?</i>

581
00:41:30,321 --> 00:41:32,755
<i>When one door closes,</i>
<i>another window opens.</i>

582
00:41:33,290 --> 00:41:35,019
Tommy. Get in.

583
00:41:35,726 --> 00:41:37,216
If you don't mind,
I'd just like to walk.

584
00:41:37,728 --> 00:41:39,355
Hey, put him in the trunk.

585
00:41:40,464 --> 00:41:41,431
I'm getting in.

586
00:41:54,678 --> 00:41:56,737
I guess you heard,
somebody

587
00:41:57,681 --> 00:41:59,410
