588
00:42:00,451 --> 00:42:02,351
Yeah, I heard.
I'm really sorry.

589
00:42:03,554 --> 00:42:06,148
You know, I can understand
somebody wanting to kill Huey.

590
00:42:06,590 --> 00:42:08,057
He had enemies.

591
00:42:08,425 --> 00:42:09,824
Who doesn't, right?

592
00:42:11,228 --> 00:42:14,163
I just can't figure out
what he was doing
in Sal Minnetta's basement.

593
00:42:14,899 --> 00:42:16,890
He didn't tell anyone?

594
00:42:17,268 --> 00:42:20,396
I mean, the last thing
anybody knows,
he went to visit you

595
00:42:20,471 --> 00:42:22,336
and your brother
at the hospital.

596
00:42:23,140 --> 00:42:24,801
Brought you the pie
his wife made.

597
00:42:25,843 --> 00:42:27,242
Yeah, he came by.

598
00:42:27,444 --> 00:42:29,036
He was checking on Sean.

599
00:42:29,179 --> 00:42:32,478
I heard that Sean took
quite a beating.

600
00:42:32,850 --> 00:42:34,078
Is he okay?

601
00:42:34,451 --> 00:42:35,748
He's gonna be okay.

602
00:42:37,388 --> 00:42:38,548
That's good.

603
00:42:39,857 --> 00:42:41,984
That's good you still
got your brother.

604
00:42:44,428 --> 00:42:46,828
Did Huey say anything to you
before he left the hospital?

605
00:42:47,531 --> 00:42:49,362
Where he was going?

606
00:42:49,833 --> 00:42:51,061
Anything?

607
00:42:51,168 --> 00:42:52,601
I wish I could tell you more.

608
00:42:55,539 --> 00:42:56,870
Me, too.

609
00:42:58,142 --> 00:42:59,541
All right,
get out of here.

610
00:43:03,414 --> 00:43:04,711
Hey.

611
00:43:05,516 --> 00:43:07,507
You hear anything,
all right?

612
00:43:11,789 --> 00:43:13,279
I'll let you know.

613
00:43:14,558 --> 00:43:15,889
Good.

